# simd_packed_ulong4

**Type Alias**

A packed vector of four 64-bit unsigned integer elements.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias simd_packed_ulong4 = SIMD4<simd_ulong1>
```

## Alternative Type Alias

- **packed_ulong4**

## Packed Vector Data Types

- **simd_packed_ulong2**: A packed vector of two 64-bit unsigned integer element.
- **simd_packed_ulong8**: A packed vector of eight 64-bit unsigned integer elements.
